	  parser.c, parser.h: [lcd4linux @ 2000-03-18 10:31:06 by reinelt]
	  added sensor handling (for temperature etc.)
	  made data collecting happen only if data is used
	  (reading /proc/meminfo takes a lot of CPU!)
